long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows users to inspect Virtual DOM in Bobril (https://github.com/Bobris/Bobril) based applications. When chrome dev console is opened and you select element on page that uses Bobril. Then on each click on element, Bobril tab in dev tools tabs is updated and shows current virtual node information.
